sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServe as KServe Ingress<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant API as vLLM OpenAI API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant ZMQ as MQLLMEngine<br/>ZeroMQ IPC
    participant Engine as vLLM Engine<br/>(V1 AsyncLLM)
    participant GPU as GPU Workers<br/>CUDA/ROCm
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: OpenAI-Compatible Inference Request

    Client->>KServe: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    KServe->>API: Forward (cluster-internal)<br/>HTTP/8000, Optional Bearer Token
    API->>ZMQ: Forward via ZeroMQ IPC<br/>Unix domain socket
    ZMQ->>Engine: Process inference request
    Engine->>GPU: Execute model inference<br/>NCCL for multi-GPU
    GPU-->>Engine: Inference result
    Engine-->>ZMQ: Response
    ZMQ-->>API: Response
    API-->>KServe: JSON/SSE Response<br/>(streaming or non-streaming)
    KServe-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: gRPC Inference (TGIS Adapter)

    participant TGIS as TGIS gRPC Adapter<br/>8033/TCP gRPC

    Client->>KServe: gRPC Request<br/>TLS 1.2+
    KServe->>TGIS: gRPC/8033<br/>plaintext (cluster-internal)
    TGIS->>API: HTTP/8000 (internal)
    API->>ZMQ: ZeroMQ IPC
    ZMQ->>Engine: Process request
    Engine->>GPU: Model inference
    GPU-->>Engine: Result
    Engine-->>ZMQ: Response
    ZMQ-->>API: Response
    API-->>TGIS: HTTP Response
    TGIS-->>KServe: gRPC Response
    KServe-->>Client: gRPC Response (TLS)

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Model Loading (Startup)

    Engine->>HF: Download model<br/>HTTPS/443, HF Token auth
    HF-->>Engine: Model artifacts
    Engine->>S3: Download model (alternative)<br/>HTTPS/443, S3 credentials
    S3-->>Engine: Model artifacts
    Engine->>GPU: Load model to GPU memory<br/>PCIe/NVLink
